title: Henrique scores twice, Devils beat Sabres 4-3
text:
Published By: Charlotte Observer: Sports - Today 
Adam Henrique scored twice and added an assist and the New Jersey Devils won their fourth straight with a 4-3 victory over the Buffalo Sabre...
